data.description: Spacious 1939 stick-built home that is centrally located. The home offers 2,193 sq ft of living space, with three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The spacious primary suite features a walk-in shower, secondary closet, walk in shower, separate tub, and laundry. There is a large pantry that could be converted into an office or possibly a 4th bedroom. Family room, living room and large utility with sink and storage. Detached 720 sq ft garage with storage, 14x20 carport and in the front, you have an 11x20 carport. Fenced in yard with underground sprinklers and an irrigation well add to the appeal.
